data.description:
Introducing a charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in the heart of Olathe, Kansas, ready to welcome its new owners. 
Step into a home that has been thoughtfully updated throughout, featuring newer windows, roof, HVAC and water heater for modern comfort and efficiency. This meticulously remodeled residence boasts an open floor plan, creating a seamless flow between its inviting spaces. The attention to detail in the renovations is evident, creating a contemporary yet warm atmosphere.  The main bedroom comes complete with an attached bathroom, offering both convenience and privacy. Nestled on a lot that backs to woods, enjoy the tranquility of nature right in your backyard. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home – a perfect blend of comfort, style, and the serenity of a wooded backdrop. Schedule a visit today and discover the charm of living in this beautifully updated Olathe residence.
